# Global settings
SyncState *
Expunge None

# Averagehaskeller
IMAPAccount averagehaskeller
Host imap.gmail.com
User averagehaskeller@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg --no-tty -dq /Users/adinapoli/Dropbox/dotfiles/.authinfo.json.gpg | jq -r .email.averagehaskellerGmail.password"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/cert.pem
AuthMech XOAUTH2

IMAPStore remote-averagehaskeller
Account averagehaskeller

MaildirStore local-averagehaskeller
Path ~/mail/averagehaskeller/

Channel averagehaskeller
Master :remote-averagehaskeller:
Slave :local-averagehaskeller:
Patterns *
Create Slave
CopyArrivalDate yes

